Dawai: Okay, well there you have it, everybody. A whole list of stuff that could be springing up for you, could be oscillating through your awareness, and it just shows you I think, that everything's included, all right? That no matter how you feel, that you don't need to judge yourself, you don't need to change it, you don't need to go into this deep psychoanalysis of yourself, psychoanalysis, excuse me. 

And you don't need to do anything about it, especially in the 10 minute sessions that we do, the silent stillness, we don't want to do anything about our body, our feelings, our thoughts, and our environment---whatever shape they may be taking. Making sense, right? Have I hammered it in your head enough? Go ahead...

